EXTRACTED VALUE: For half the price of most 360 games, you get one of world’s most original games in a long long time and one of the best 360 games to boot as well.
It's not just a classic game, it's an essential purchase – no matter which version you decide to get it for.
It provides a highly enjoyable single-player campaign, and improves upon a standard set by the first 3D Ninja Gaiden game four years ago.
An extremely impressive balance of considerable complexity, Viva Piñata provides an experience unlike any other on the Xbox 360.
This game is rock solid with some of the most spectacular and fast paced gameplay.
Overall Battlefield Bad Company is a great game and a step up from the previous Battlefield title on the 360.
